{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-05-29-how-to-add-flag-icon-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aHoisting! To add flag icon in react js, you can use . It will add flag icon in react js. Today, I am going to show you, how to add‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To add flag icon in react js, you can use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Flag code=\"IND\" height=\"16\" /></code>. It will add flag icon in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add flag icon in react js.</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the following packages to use flag icon in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npm install react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>world<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>flags\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">yarn add react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>world<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>flags\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import react component.</h3>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Flag <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-world-flags'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Create a Component.</h3>\n<p>You can use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Flag code=\"IND\" height=\"16\" /></code> to add flag icon in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h3<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Country Flag<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h3<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Flag code<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"IND\"</span> height<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"16\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Define the add flag icon example.</h3>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">'react-world-flags'</code> and use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Flag code=\"IND\" height=\"16\" /></code> to add flag icon in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Flag <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-world-flags'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h3<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Country Flag<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h3<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Flag code<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"IND\"</span> height<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"16\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">OR</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> IndiaFlag <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./india.webp'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Country Flag<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>IndiaFlag<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"INDIA Flag\"</span> style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'50px'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'auto'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">code=\"IND\"</code> and add flag icon in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Flag-icon</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 322px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d50287ed79c92f8daee0ef577521696f/ce133/flag-icon.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 96.20253164556962%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRmAAAABXRUJQVlA4IFQAAACwAwCdASoUABMAPtFcpU0oJSOiMBgIAQAaCWUAzYQQ6ceZ+FVXQAD9U/hsMmq3RwWRwSdRx9U2ZDdWX1C3vOLvXpyIPLaA0wsyEGbsnuCcnqAAAAA='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, add, flag icon\"\n        title=\"React, add, flag icon\"\n        src=\"/static/d50287ed79c92f8daee0ef577521696f/ce133/flag-icon.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d50287ed79c92f8daee0ef577521696f/81b7c/flag-icon.webp 158w,\n/static/d50287ed79c92f8daee0ef577521696f/6ea66/flag-icon.webp 315w,\n/static/d50287ed79c92f8daee0ef577521696f/ce133/flag-icon.webp 322w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 322px) 100vw, 322px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Flag-image</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 367px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7807879c331a774a43547e6f4c817ffd/ddb01/flag-image.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 71.51898734177216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRmgAAABXRUJQVlA4IFwAAADQAwCdASoUAA4APtFUo0uoJKMhsAgBABoJQBOj+ABicQB2anaC5MAAy0+gRMgV2BDHjto/tzQXlfRc20NszshMSmwQwQxr77ACQwebd3DuYFc4DY6xqH6BnQAAAA=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, add, flag icon\"\n        title=\"React, add, flag icon\"\n        src=\"/static/7807879c331a774a43547e6f4c817ffd/ddb01/flag-image.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7807879c331a774a43547e6f4c817ffd/81b7c/flag-image.webp 158w,\n/static/7807879c331a774a43547e6f4c817ffd/6ea66/flag-image.webp 315w,\n/static/7807879c331a774a43547e6f4c817ffd/ddb01/flag-image.webp 367w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 367px) 100vw, 367px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to add flag icon in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"May 29, 2024","description":"Example of add flag icon in react js with step by step tutorial - aHoisting","social_image":{"absolutePath":"/Users/mac/Documents/hoisting/ahoisting/static/media/template/reactjs.jpg"}}},"pr